translate ru UnionKingdom13_d44aedfd:
    # "In the weeks that followed, the decisions that had been made during their Union Council were slowly disseminated."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4139fc57:
    # "Laws rewritten. Orders handed down."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_f7e9dacf:
    # "Step-by-step, the disparate kingdoms of the Union came together."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_a4ea9f0a:
    # "What had been driven apart in centuries would not be forged together in years, but the first steps had been undertaken."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_0a252d3a:
    # "Out of the many decisions, there was one that weighed heavier than most."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_1c8eb71b:
    # "Sarah's election as leader of the Union."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_cc89befe:
    # "Gathered from every corner of the Union, all the greatest people of import had been brought into the throne room."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_052ceca4:
    # "Here she would speak her words and they would swear their oaths."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_f331f667:
    # "Sarah looked across the room and saw the sea of faces."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_75ff0abe:
    # "Even in Rosanna, she had struggled to know every name of every noble; but here it was impossible to even attempt."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_67c1fd62:
    # "She would soon rule so many..."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4d69bfda:
    # "The power of it might have seduced many others, but to Sarah, it only weighed on her shoulders like stones."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_9f569f9c:
    # "Her every movement felt heavy and slow. She was careful with her every utterance and even policed her own thoughts."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_8e1c6df2:
    # "To be burdened with a power like this...she had never set out to seek it, but it had fallen on her all the same."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_5d480976:
    # "Yet there was nothing to enjoy."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_615e8aed:
    # "The earliest reports of the Mythran invasion had solidified."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_2b7c2363:
    # "From rumors, to reports, they now knew that the two legions were close to complete."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_09a15e36:
    # "They would land on their shores. Very soon."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_3456f820:
    # "Sarah drew in her breath and tried to steady herself."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_a102672b:
    # "She was the face of their Union. If she wavered, so would all of them."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_3866476c:
    # "A loud bell rang out and the murmurs in the room were brought to silence."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_b7b895c2:
    # "So quiet, Sarah imagined she could hear her own heartbeat."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_50f263e5:
    # "Slowly she strode out to the front of the hall."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4d4e5fbe:
    # "Cloaked in the regalia of her house, as well as the sigils of the other nations; Sarah stood before the host that had gathered."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_d0bf6da7:
    # "All their eyes fell on her."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_67c26157:
    # "Sarah allowed her eyes to roam across the room."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_f653f864:
    # "All these faces. These people that now looked to her for leadership."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4764c0c4:
    # "Sarah straightend her back, put out her shoulders and tilted her head."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_fdee2c5b:
    # "She drew in a final breath. Then she spoke."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_0ba9bf1e:
    # s "Before me is gathered a host unlike any other. Representing the unified strength of our Union, not seen in centuries."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_822e6075:
    # s "From you, to me, will flow the authority to speak with a single voice for all of us."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_9887155d:
    # s "Our Union faces an external threat the likes of which we have not seen in the lifetime of any present here."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_219cb4fb:
    # s "And it is these historical times that call on us to make historic changes."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_3ffb8752:
    # s "We shall leave the centuries of division behind and move forward as a singular people."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_be51f54b:
    # s "But before we can lay claim to our sovereignty, we shall first be called to defend it."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_7b593d45:
    # s "The Mythran armies, two legions in total, will soon land on our shores."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_44f67c8a:
    # s "If we fall apart as he have in our past, they shall seek to put us against on another."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_407bfe40:
    # s "Only by holding onto each other, can we have have any hope of saving ourselves."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_24b1d8cf:
    # s "It is under these dire circumstances that I will be crowned today."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_ff43245a:
    # s "I speak them not to put fear into your hearts."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_5b57568f:
    # s "Rather, I say these words to remind all of us of the unprecedented times in which we find ourselves."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_95fe10c0:
    # s "And to prepare each of us, for the sacrifices that await."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_b1b2b8bb:
    # "Sarah raised up one hand."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_16297e2e:
    # s "Before all the Gods known to the Pantheon, I swear my oaths to you and the Union that you represent."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_a2bb6302:
    # s "I swear, that not with joy, but with great reluctance, I take upon myself the title of old."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_bb9021d5:
    # s "High Queen of the Union."
    s ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_5ac94613:
    # "As one, all of the people gathered in the hall leapt to their feet."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_416920f9:
    # "A rapturous applause exploded, echoing loudly against the walls of the castle."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_b6717ae3:
    # "Stomping their feet, Sarah could feel the very foundations of the construct shake."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_9288971d:
    # "Their enemy was coming for them, but in this moment, Sarah was for a brief moment, unafraid."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4360bce5:
    # "For now, this is where the story ends."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4360bce5_1:
    # "For now, this is where the story ends."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom13_4360bce5_2:
    # "For now, this is where the story ends."
    ""

